        nmap <silent> <A-k> :wincmd k<CR>
        nmap <silent> <A-l> :wincmd l<CR>

        " If your '{' or '}' are not in the first column, and you would like to use "[["
        " and "]]" anyway, try these mappings: >
        nmap [[ ?{<CR>
